title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update X USA - Eugene
description:
In this video we will fly over the city of Eugene which is located on the West Coast of the US close to Portland. We start the video from the airport of Eugene (KEUG) which is located in North West from the city. After making a turn to the right we make multiple flights over the city while looking and the photogrammetry content which has been added as part of World Update X.
